# Generation Metadata Tagging

When generating or modifying code files, append a metadata block as a comment
at the end of each file using the appropriate comment syntax.

## Python / Ruby / Shell / YAML
```
# --- AI Generation Metadata ---
# model_id: <your model identifier>
# model_family: <your model family>
# cursor_mode: <agent|composer|chat|background-agent>
# timestamp: <ISO 8601 UTC>
# sod_status: PENDING_INDEPENDENT_REVIEW
# ---
```

## JavaScript / TypeScript / Java / C / C++ / Go / Rust
