# ---
```

## Field Descriptions

| Field | Description |
|---|---|
| `model_id` | Exact model name (e.g., `claude-sonnet-4-5`, `gpt-4o`, `gemini-2.5-pro`) |
| `model_family` | Family grouping for SoD (e.g., `anthropic-claude`, `openai-gpt`) |
| `cursor_mode` | Which Cursor interaction mode produced the code |
| `timestamp` | ISO 8601 UTC generation timestamp |
| `sod_status` | Always `PENDING_INDEPENDENT_REVIEW` at generation time |

## Cursor Mode Values

- `agent` — Cursor Agent mode (interactive, auto-executes tool calls)
- `chat` — Cursor Chat mode (conversational, no auto-execution)
- `background-agent` — Cursor Background Agent (async cloud VM execution)
- `composer` — Legacy Composer mode (pre-Cursor 2.0)
